comments: I took her for three math classes and LOVED her! I was horrible and I mean HORRIBLE at math until I got into get her class. She\'s picky about how you show work but as long as you show that you\'re trying she will NOT let you fail her class.

THE best teacher at the college. All you have to do is follow instructions and you will do well. Anyone that complains about her apparently has issues. Only teacher in the area that knows what the heck she\'s talking about. A++++
Great teacher. As long as you try in her class you will be fine. However you have to do everything her way. No short cuts on any of your work.

Puts on a front of a very nice old lady but still teaches like we were in the 60\'s. We did not get along and she made sure I didnt get my A by scoring me low enough on my final that I ended up with an 89.4 average. VERY VINDICTIVE...
She is a great teacher and extremely helpful if you\'re willing to attempt anything you will probably still pass. I reccommend her! She is rather picky though but it\'s worth it!

If you are willing to do things exactly and precisely her way, you will succeed in the class. She is very picky about how you show your work, but she is very helpful and pleasant. She wants you to succeed in her class. She is happy to work after class if you need extra help.
